title: may 16: when clones attack (with Quinn Christopherson)
description:
In this episode of 365 days with mxmtoon, Maia talks about the release of Star Wars Episode II: The Attack of the Clones, the second of Star Wars creator George Lucas’s much-anticipated and oft-maligned prequels. After, she’s joined by guest Quinn Christopherson. Listen to this episode today and make sure you’re following along with the daily updates @365daysmxmtoon on all platforms.
